overview: In this corner: hot-assed, hot-blooded Latina Franceska Jaimes. In that corner: hugely hung superstud/filthy filmmaker Nacho Vidal. The director's epic, new movie is dedicated to the curvy, fiery bitch, and the "Nacho vs. Franceska Jaimes" title is perhaps telling given that the combatants are real-life husband and wife! Really, all marriages need the sexual energy, variety and friction Mr. and Mrs. Vidal expose here.
title: Nacho vs Franceska Jaimes
